Finance Data Processing API

Features:

Authentication
Role Based Access
CRUD Transactions
Filtering
Pagination
Dashboard Analytics

Tech Stack:

FastAPI
SQLAlchemy
SQLite

Run:

pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn app.main:app --reload

Endpoints:

POST /users
POST /users/login
POST /transactions
GET /transactions
PUT /transactions/{id}
DELETE /transactions/{id}
GET /dashboard/summary
